<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Access Denied | Full Stack Café</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-red: #b91c1c;
            --text-dark: #1f2937;
            --text-light: #6b7280;
            --bg-gray: #f3f4f6;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-gray);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 8px 10px -6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 90%;
        }

        .icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: block;
        }

        h2 {
            color: var(--text-dark);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
        }

        p {
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .back-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: var(--primary-red);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.1s ease;
        }

        .back-btn:hover {
            background-color: #991b1b;
        }

        .back-btn:active {
            transform: scale(0.98);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <span class="icon">🚫</span>
        <h2>Admin Access Required</h2>
        <p>You don't have permission to view the Canteen Command Center. Please contact the manager if you believe this is an error.</p>
        <a href="/products" class="back-btn">Go Back to Menu</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>